snippet.title: Amber Heard Allegedly Sued by Ex-Lover Elon Musk Over Frozen Embryos
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Allegedly Sued by Ex-Lover Elon Musk Over Frozen Embryos..
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChjDtGelMNkllI5S22oO_aA?sub_confirmation=1
 The Mera of DC Extended Universe is reportedly embroiled in a legal battle with the Tesla mogul over the rights to embryos they created during their relationship.  Jul 31, 2020   AceShowbiz - Amber Heard was reportedly locked in a legal battle with ex-lover Elon Musk over the "Aquaman" actress' frozen embryos.    In documents obtained by Britain's Daily Mirror newspaper, Jennifer Howell - a pal of Heard's sister Whitney Henriquez and mum Paige - revealed the latter told her that billionaire Musk was suing the actress.         "Paige told me.... she was in a legal battle with him over the rights to embryos they had created together," she shared. "He wanted to destroy them, and Amber tried to keep them to have a baby."    Comparing Musk to Heard's ex-husband Johnny Depp, Howell said, "Paige told me that Johnny was either an angel or a saint compared to Elon."    Howell made the claims in a U.S. libel trial Depp has brought against Heard, and her statement will be used as evidence in the ...
